Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:45.08,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm starting at the preliminaries for\Nthe pro exam again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Iijima-kun quit the Insei program already,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'm at my limit, too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, have you heard, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A few players from the Kyuuseikai have gone\Nto China to study and to further relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Isumi-kun went with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:12.82,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,370,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(325,115)}The Sixty-Fifth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:12.82,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx340\t(0,370,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Isumi no Go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.28,Background,,0,0,0,,It only takes four hours to\Ngo from Tokyo to Bei'jing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.87,Background,,0,0,0,,Are we taking a taxi the rest of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.54,Background,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to get\Nto the Go Institute of China?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Half an hour I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.88,Background,,0,0,0,,What? Sakurano and Isumi, is this the\Nfirst time in China for both of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Isumi, when you quit the Kyuuseikai last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were giving up on becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he give it up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan would play evenly with your average pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said he wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had gotten depressed\Nand given it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be alone for a bit\Nto organize my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Master Narusara invited\Nyou to this Shinzen match,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,shows that he thinks highly of your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to pass this year, in order to\Nthank the teacher for his kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.38,Background,,0,0,0,,You really do! You're already nineteen, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't become a pro until I was over twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurano is Sakurano, Isumi is Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.72,Background,,0,0,0,,How many games are we playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.39,Background,,0,0,0,,Three games or so over three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The pro exam preliminaries will start in two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend that the Shinzen match is the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.20,Background,,0,0,0,,This move you made was rather peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost all the stones you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I couldn't turn the game around after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:06.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a bad game. Don't feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's cheer up with a nice lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am dissatisfied with that game I just played.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not depressed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just angry at myself for playing too\Naggressively, because I thought I couldn't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For not being able to play my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could have won if you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck on your afternoon match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I once pretended to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,play a Go stone in this park...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai found a rock that looked like a Go stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.82,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup something just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And he told me to try playing this stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The rock flew out of my hand\Nwhen I tried to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.05,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Morishita is furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't come to the study sessions, and\Nyou've been ditching the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't said anything to\Nthe Go Institute have you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Are you in a slump? Or are you\Njust tired of it all already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.78,Background,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.46,Background,,0,0,0,,How can I know what you're thinking\Nif you don't say anything!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,How can I tell him that I don't care about Go anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I want to see Sai again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I started living on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All our Insei friends come to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come, too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one that's standing still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I played three Ooteai matches,\Nand I'm two and one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ochi has already played four games\Nand has four straight wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-san, Komiya, and everyone else are working\Nhard for this year's pro exams, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, Isumi-san went\Nto play Go against Chinese pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san is in China?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We just barely passed last year, even though\NIsumi-san was taking the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san will definitely pass this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:57.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell Isumi-san that you've been\Nditching all the matches when he becomes a pro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel ashamed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.94,Background,,0,0,0,,You want to play Go, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.23,Background,,0,0,0,,You want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.48,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm going first, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.53,Background,,0,0,0,,16-4,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You just though about where to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the response that you came up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.96,Background,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.43,Background,,0,0,0,,Three days and two nights passes by like a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.23,Background,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to say goodbye to\NLiu Xian Sheng and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time? Let's go see Tien an men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I'm going to come all the way to China\Njust to look around stores, right Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.91,Background,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for brining this up at the last minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to stay another day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play him one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm going shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll stay behind by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Him... You mean Zhao-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to beat him, but\Nit was a very close game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to play that well at his age...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.94,Background,,0,0,0,,He really showed me how strong\Nthe Go Institute of China is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.49,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi, haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pros here were chosen out of the pros.
Comment: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:41.13,NoteArial,,0,0,10,,Same as 11:07. Don't think it has a shadow. They likely just changed the colours since font 17.5 is an exact match and normal notes also don't have shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:41.13,NoteArial,,0,0,10,,{\fs20\1c&H6FE6D7&\shad0\3c&H24696C&\fad(0,501)}'Zhong Guo Go Institute'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:43.25,Background,,0,0,0,,China has pro players in every Sheng...\Nin Japanese that means "prefecture".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.71,Background,,0,0,0,,Anyone that is thought to have potential out of all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.97,Background,,0,0,0,,is gathered here in Bei'jing to get daily training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.13,Background,,0,0,0,,They live here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.76,Background,,0,0,0,,What!? They live here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:59.44,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, people who make a lot,\Nor people who get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.48,Background,,0,0,0,,seem to rent apartments nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:07.35,Background,,0,0,0,,There are only thirty or so young pros\Nwho are in their teens and twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is one of the chosen pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's living here, far away from\Nhis parents, at that age...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.32,Background,,0,0,0,,He's an exceptional child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.95,Background,,0,0,0,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.21,Background,,0,0,0,,I don't think he goes to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.92,Background,,0,0,0,,They have enough time for\Na normal education, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, they're already pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.76,Background,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Li Xian Sheng. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he said that he'd like\Nto play Zhao-kun again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Play Zhao again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't accept the fact that\Nhe lost to Zhao yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun played well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zhao neutralized his attack very effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how Isumi-kun feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't care how good he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back to Japan while I'm\Nstill angry at myself for losing a game
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,that I did not do my best on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't, if I want to be confident\Nduring the pro exams this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zhao is going to be gone starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.47,Background,,0,0,0,,There is a match in a rural\Narea, so he headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.72,Background,,0,0,0,,He should be back in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, why don't you study here\Nfor a few days until he comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.94,Background,,0,0,0,,The playing room here is a place\Nfor pros to train themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.40,Background,,0,0,0,,Everyone gathers there everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play however much you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry at yourself for losing\Nto Zhao. I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no need to be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Li Xian Sheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone willing to work hard is welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.75,Background,,0,0,0,,Get a room in a nearby hotel, and come study here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Isumi. What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It might be a good opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you for letting me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:12.07,NoteArial,,0,0,10,,{\fs20\1c&H6FE6D7&\shad0\3c&H24696C&\fad(0,501)}'Zhong Guo Go Institute'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.39,Background,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.23,Background,,0,0,0,,It's a place where all the best pros gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.19,Background,,0,0,0,,But it is a very strict place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.40,Background,,0,0,0,,You're sent back to the rural provinces\Nif you don't do well in your matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.75,Background,,0,0,0,,There are people who don't improve as much as\Nexpected, even if they have a lot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Xian Sheng manages both the studying of\NGo and the lifestyles of the players here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the playing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You research new moves here, replay\Nold games, play practice games...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.67,Background,,0,0,0,,It's a place of learning for the chosen pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,They're all young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A study session for Chinese pros...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Don't feel out of place! I studied\Nwith pros at Kyuuseikai, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They study here starting from\N8:15 in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you playing hooky again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always do that when I'm not around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't playing hooky. I just\Nwent to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.12,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name of a friend of mine in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks just like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Xian Sheng? What's "Waya"?\NIs he talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Isumi-kun from Japan. He's\Ngoing to be studying here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.06,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.15,Background,,0,0,0,,A Japanese pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. He is someone who is just starting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet.... you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.36,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun! Isumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Waya have an outtie just like me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's already lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.00,Background,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a problem child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping isn't very motivated to study Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Xian Sheng must be annoyed with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always yelling at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pro too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He came here last year at the age of eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we eat, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Eat here on the first floor while you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Everyone eats here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.21,Background,,0,0,0,,You should go and get a hotel room\Nas soon as you finish eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two hours for lunch. That's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be a long time, but if you work\Nhard, you will learn something valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Le Ping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can't be relaxing just because\NI met a small version of Waya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to play a game with one and\Na half hours each in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're playing in leagues right now\Nto test out everyone's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.25,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll write your name in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the members of the lower\Ndan group, first dan through 3-dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.30,Background,,0,0,0,,You should play anyone who's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:22.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Li Xian Sheng,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Isumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Le Ping...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't be losing to a child like him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I underestimated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I belittled him too much in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Le Ping is one of the chosen pros, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, you were too forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.99,Background,,0,0,0,,This move was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like Black avoided White's attack well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it lost out during the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think that this would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose, not to the likes of you, Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He laughed...! At me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.29,Background,,0,0,0,,This is a situation where you should move\Nto the sides instead of towards the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Black has strength on the\Ntop side and the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Everything they say is brilliant and well thought out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't join the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been working here for months... no, years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In a place where everyone around them is the\Nelite of the pros... from dawn until dusk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:39.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be a good opportunity\Nfor me to learn here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:44.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... if this place just serves to make\Nme lose confidence in myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No. It's still all right when I'm angry at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If my self-anger were to turn into self-pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The best of the pros in their teens and twenties...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The elite of the pros who are stronger\Nthan players who are older than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What can I accomplish here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.09,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play a game of speed Go?\NWith ten seconds per move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:22.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I played ten second Go a lot in my free time at\Nboth Kyuuseikai and the Insei study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It depends on instinct and ideas,\Nrather than reading ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's around my age...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But he's as strong as...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,a 9-dan pro from Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,White can pull back if Black plays a hane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but that would kill his cluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So White can only cut and play elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Black loses the initiative, but he has no\Nweaknesses, so he has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I thought he'd simply pull back,\Nbut he has to play elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I resigned too early...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's play again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you came from Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in my room all day today,\Nso I just heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Yang Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A nearby hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:01.08,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm in a double, so there's an empty bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Wanna stay there? Room 303.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought foreigners were not allowed to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Who would know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Xian Sheng always leaves by five.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make you pay rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to spend some time alone at the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm not staying long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could tell me about\Nthe entertainment industry in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess someone who's here to study\NGo wouldn't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm done for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In the pro exam last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was able to recover after losing three games in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,to Shindou, Waya, and Fuku only because\Nof my determination to beat Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My Go supports me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll believe in my own capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was able to tell myself that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:19.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... will I be able to tell myself\Nthe same thing here in China?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Will my Go support me here?
